                "next": {
                  "id": 2
                },
                "speaker": "The Citizen",
                "text": "How does one define 'exotic'? My family has bred bettas for many years. Now we are forced onto the black market."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "notes": ""
    },
    {
